OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fto the evening with clear spells.
OL,7,FShowers returning through the night
OL,8,Fwhich could become heavy at times
OL,9,Fduring the early morning. Most places
OL,10,Fstaying frost free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,13,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,14,Fheavy with the added risk of hail in
OL,15,Fplaces. Chilly, with temperatures
OL,16,Fbelow average. Windy for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
