OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying unsettled on Thursday with
OL,7,Fsome showery rain, and brisk winds.
OL,8,FDrier and brighter on Friday and
OL,9,FSaturday, with winds easing.
OL,10,FTemperatures staying below average for
OL,11,Fthe time of year.
